ight: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 203pt;&quot;&gt;/card_transactions/transactions&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;50&quot; class=&quot;xl547&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 38pt;&quot;&gt;GET&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;242&quot; class=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 182pt;&quot;&gt;cardTransactions[].orderDateTime&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;49&quot; class=&quot;xl779&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-align: center; width: 37pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;88&quot; class=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 66pt;&quot;&gt;string($date-time)&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;215&quot; class=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 161pt;&quot;&gt;Date and time when the transaction occurred.&lt;br&gt;The value uses the complete data format defined in ISO 8601:&lt;br&gt;&#39;YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssTZD&#39;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Where:&lt;br&gt;YYYY: 4-digit year&lt;br&gt;MM: 2-digit month (for example, 01 = January)&lt;br&gt;DD: 2-digit day of the month (01 through 31)&lt;br&gt;hh: 2-digit hour of the day (00 through 23)&lt;br&gt;mm: 2-digit minute of the hour (00 through 59)&lt;br&gt;ss.sss: 5-digit seconds and milliseconds, separated by a point&lt;br&gt;TZD: Time zone indicator&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;89&quot; class=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 67pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;516&quot; class=&quot;xl1870&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 387pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font187&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8pt;&quot;&gt;Por cada deviceId que se obtenga del Cliente en la respuesta de la API /life-cycle/devices/origin-persons/{originPerson}/details).&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Se debe buscar en esta API Card Transactions, los card_id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font188&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8pt; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font187&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8pt;&quot;&gt;y obtener la ultima fecha de operación/transacción que se realizo en el Contrato&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;- Se debe ordenar por el atributo &quot;cardTransactions[].orderDateTime&quot; de forma ascendente y tomar la fecha más reciente (Si el API ya viene ordenada, hacer caso omiso a este paso)&lt;br&gt;- Si no hay una fecha de operación/transacción en un lapso del mes en curso + 3 meses, se devolverá una fecha default &quot;0001-01-01&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;209&quot; class=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 157pt;&quot;&gt;Convertir formato: 2023-03-26T17:32:28.123Z a formato YYYY-MM-DD&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Formato de respuesta: YYYY-MM-DD&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;189&quot; class=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 142pt;&quot;&gt;A esta API se ingresa por card_contract_id, dato que ya se obtuvo con el API &quot;/devices/origin-persons/{originPerson}/details&quot; y atributo &quot;contract.devices[].subContractId&quot;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr height=&quot;31&quot; style=&quot;height: 23.25pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;105&quot; height=&quot;31&quot; class=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 79pt; height: 23.25pt;&quot;&gt;Cadastral-domain-api&lt;br&gt;Card Security&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;270&quot; class=&quot;xl563&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 203pt;&quot;&gt;/jwks&lt;br&gt;/card_security/{cardId}/restricted_data&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;50&quot; class=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 38pt;&quot;&gt;GET&lt;br&gt;POST&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl378&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;pan&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl378&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl378&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;string&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;215&quot; class=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 161pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl378&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Requerido&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;516&quot; class=&quot;xl1974&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 387pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font187&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8pt;&quot;&gt;Se obtiene el PAN usando las APIS de jwks y cardData. regresar el ultimo PAN de la lista para lograr la paginación&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font189&quot; style=&quot;color: red; font-size: 8pt; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Se realizará la paginación y la ejecución dual (validar como se hizo en la trx.LMWT)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl378&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;189&quot; class=&quot;xl547&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 142pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
