lass=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 200pt;&quot;&gt;CONSULTA CLAVE BANCARIA ESTANDARIZADA&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl378&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl378&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;CLABE&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl542&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;18&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl1858&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;string&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;211&quot; class=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 158pt;&quot;&gt;Clave bancaria estandarizada&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl378&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;317&quot; class=&quot;xl163&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 238pt;&quot;&gt;La consulta se realiza por cuenta y puede capturarse de 11 posiciones o 23 (entidad [4], centro alta [4], cuenta [12], divisa [3])&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl378&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;B485 - CLABE&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;299&quot; class=&quot;xl1870&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 224pt;&quot;&gt;Obtener del formato de salida LMMWHS1 de esta Trx. los campos: ENTIDAD + CENTRO + CUENTA + MONEDA y utilizarlos como entrada en el campo CCCDIV (COD.CTA-CLIENTE-DIV) de la Trx.B485&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
